Share of crop area receiving fertilizer and fertilizer use per receiving acre, by nutrient, are presented for the major producing States for corn, cotton, soybeans, and wheat. Additional data include fertilizer farm prices and indices of wholesale fertilizer price. Fertilizer price data are through 2013.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>consumption</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>corn</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>cotton</dcat:keyword>
